 Ultra Magnus couldnt stand the sight of the destroyed ship. He opened his 
mind and the oracal appereaded around him. He opened a message to 
them...."Come my fellow cybertronians. We have very little time. I alone have 
the blue prints to fix the ark. If we do not the entire world and time will 
be destroyed. Kit Kat....Prowl...Cereberus....Valtron.....Sphink   come and 
bring who is willing. Please all time and space rest in your hands."
